data.description: Move-In Ready Home with lender incentive, ask for details! Enjoy energy efficiency and savings with the included Solar Panels PLUS Washer, Dryer, New Water softener. Beautiful two story home in Candlewood. This home offers 4 bedroom, 2.5 full baths. Kitchen has been recently updated featuring clean grey cabinet, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. Features an inviting & open floor plan with an abundance of natural light. Greenbelt home site perfect for entertaining. New carpet throughout the upstairs. Bonus Room area upstairs perfect for office, playroom, or additional living space. Schedule a showing today!
